#EXTM3U
# ============================================================================
#  SabiStream demo playlist — Live TV + Movies + Series in one M3U
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Purpose: a clean, copyright-safe playlist for Google Play review and QA. It
#  contains ONLY developer test streams and Creative Commons / open-movie demo
#  assets. No paid TV, no cable/satellite rebroadcasts, no PPV, no sports, no
#  premium channels, no broadcaster names.
#
#  How the three tabs are populated (matches standard panel conventions):
#    • Live TV  — entries whose group-title is a normal channel group.
#    • Movies   — entries whose group-title contains "Movies".
#    • Series   — entries whose group-title is "Series" AND whose name carries
#                 an episode marker like S01E01; episodes are grouped by the
#                 show title (the text before the SxxEyy token).
#
#  Open-movie attribution (Creative Commons — keep this in your store/testing
#  docs): "Big Buck Bunny", "Sintel", and "Tears of Steel" are Blender
#  Foundation open movies (CC BY 3.0), www.blender.org. The remaining links are
#  vendor HLS test streams (Apple, Mux, Unified Streaming, Google/Shaka,
#  CloudFront demo assets) used here purely for playback testing.
# ============================================================================

# ----------------------------- LIVE TV ------------------------------------
